meta {
  name: Update Graph Version
  type: http
  seq: 9
}

patch {
  url: {{host}}/agent-playground/graphs/:id/versions/:version_id/
  body: json
  auth: bearer
}

params:path {
  id: {{graph_id}}
  version_id: {{version_id}}
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{access_token}}
}

body:json {
  {
    "status": "active",
    "commit_message": "Promoting draft to active version"
  }
}

vars:pre-request {
  graph_id: 05fed664-761a-4355-ae8e-fa8616cf8861
  version_id: 8b267ef1-e37e-43ed-89c5-c77d4b4c6535
}

docs {
  # Update Graph Version (Metadata Only)

  **Metadata-only update endpoint.** Updates version status (promote draft to active) and/or commit message.

  **Content changes (nodes, ports, edges, node connections) must be done via:**
  - Granular CRUD endpoints (POST/PATCH/DELETE on `/nodes/`, `/ports/`, `/node-connections/`)
  - Or create a new version with content using `POST /graphs/:id/versions/`

  ## Path Parameters
  - `id`: Graph UUID
  - `version_id`: Version UUID (must be DRAFT status)

  ## Request Body (all fields optional)

  | Field | Type | Required | Description |
  |-------|------|----------|-------------|
  | `status` | string | no | `"draft"` (default) or `"active"` (promote to active) |
  | `commit_message` | string | no | Commit message (recommended when promoting to active) |

  ## Example Payloads

  ### Example 1: Promote draft to active with commit message
  ```json
  {
    "status": "active",
    "commit_message": "Initial release with text processing pipeline"
  }
  ```

  ### Example 2: Update commit message only (keep status as draft)
  ```json
  {
    "commit_message": "Updated workflow description"
  }
  ```

  ### Example 3: Promote to active without message
  ```json
  {
    "status": "active"
  }
  ```

  ## Response (200)
  Returns the updated version with full nested structure:
  ```json
  {
    "status": true,
    "result": {
      "id": "version-uuid",
      "version_number": 2,
      "status": "active",
      "tags": [],
      "commit_message": "Initial release with text processing pipeline",
      "created_at": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z",
      "nodes": [...],
      "node_connections": [...]
    }
  }
  ```

  ## Errors
  - `400`: Version is not DRAFT (only draft versions can be updated)
  - `404`: Graph or version not found

  ## Notes
  - Only DRAFT versions can be updated
  - When promoting to `"active"`, the system validates the entire graph structure
  - Promoting to active also triggers dataset column synchronization

  ## Related Endpoints
  - **To activate an INACTIVE version** (not draft), use: `POST /graphs/:id/versions/:version_id/activate/`
  - **To update version content** (nodes, ports, edges), use granular CRUD endpoints:
    - `POST /graphs/:id/versions/:version_id/nodes/` - Create node
    - `PATCH /graphs/:id/versions/:version_id/nodes/:node_id/` - Update node
    - `DELETE /graphs/:id/versions/:version_id/nodes/:node_id/` - Delete node
    - `PATCH /graphs/:id/versions/:version_id/ports/:port_id/` - Update port
    - `POST /graphs/:id/versions/:version_id/node-connections/` - Create connection
    - `DELETE /graphs/:id/versions/:version_id/node-connections/:nc_id/` - Delete connection
}
